It-tit8 kau3 Bi2-hong5 an5-an5 khiu2 goa2 e5 goa7-sann, bong goa2 e5 seng-khu, goa2 chiah hoe5-sin5--tng2-lai5, hou7-su7 sio2-chia2 ka7 i e5 chhiu2 soa2 tui3 toa7-thui2 pinn e5 chhiu2-hoann7-a2, an2-ne Bi2-hong5 chiah u7 hoat-tou7 ban2-an5 chhut-lat8. Goa2 e5 thau5-nau2 soah hiong5-hiong5 sio-phoah8--khi3, bak8-chiu cheng5 chit-e5 chiah-ni7 piann3-se3, chiah-ni7 kian-sim kap ka-ti7 senn3-mia7 hun3-tau3 e5 cha-bou2-lang5, kam2 si7 goa2 sek8-sai7 e5 hit-e5 Bi2-hong5? I kam2 cheng3-keng si7 hit-e5 put-koan2-si5 lan2-lan2 soann3-soann3, siann2-mih tai7-chi3 to beh kiann5 pin7-toann7-pou7, kiann5 khin-sang-lou7 e5 hit-e5 Bi2-hong5? Ka-ti7 sim-lai7 soah u7 chit8-e5 the2-hoe7, goan5-lai5 i si7 ka7 chit-si3-lang5 sou2-u7 e5 jim2-nai7 kap phah-piann3, long2 iong7 tui3 chia lai5--a.
Hou7-su7 sio2-chia2 siann-siann teh chhui hoah kap kou2-le7, Bi2-hong5 ma7 chit8 pai2 koh chit8 pai2 kim3-khui3 pek-lat8, khoann3 i piann3 kah kui seng-khu koann7 e5 heng5, goa2 soah siann2-mih khou2 ma7 be7-tang3 tau3 hun-tam, kan-tann e7-tang3 ka7 i e5 teng2-sin lam2 tiau5-tiau5, 2 e5 lang5 bin7 chhih8 sio-oa2, chu3-sin5 bang7 i chit8-kai2 koh chit8-kai2 chhut-lat8, ti3-su2 giong7 beh bo5-sin5--khi3 e5 bak8-chiu, sim-lai7 teh hoai5-gi5 i si7 m7-si7 e7-tang3 khoann3-tioh8 goa2 ti7 i sin-khu-pinn.
M7-chai an2-choann2, ka-ti7 soah hoe5-siong2 tioh8 10 goa7 ni5 cheng5, 2 e5 lang5 long2 iau2 siau3-lian5 e5 si5, thau5 chit8 pai2 tau3-tin7 siong-ho2 e5 tai7-chi3, nah e7 hit-chun7 e5 kam2-kak e7 ti7 chit-ma2 ui3 sim-koann-te2 ek--khi2-lai5? E7 ki3-tit hit-pai2 tai7-chi3 tann-a2 soah e5 si5, ka-ti7 kui seng-khu koann7-lau5 san-tih, pun be7 chheng-chho2 tau3-te2 si7 hann3-sio lau5 e5 koann7, ah-si7 piann3 chhin3-koann7? Tui3 hit tong-si5 iau2 koh 20 thong2 hoe3-a2 e5 ka-ti7 lai5 kong2, he si7 koe3-khi3 m7-bat tam--koe3 e5 chu-bi7, u7 keng-giam7 e5 lagn5 long2 chai-iann2, he kap song2-khoai3 chha chin hng7, lau2-sit8 kong2, sim-koann-te2 u7 chhou bat e5 kiann-hiann5, he m7-tann7 si7 lang5 kap lang5 seng-khu e5 ko-tinn5, koh-khah si7 senn3-mia7 kap senn3-mia7 teh chhiong-kek, teh chiann3-bin7 tui3-chhiang3 e5 jiat8 kap Energy, goa2 m7-bat keng-giam7--koe3, kong2 khah beng5--e5, khak-sit8 u7 tam7-poh8-a2 chih-chan3 be7-tiau5, kui-liap8 thau5-khak na2-chhiunn7 poah8 loh8 toa7-hai2 e5 tian7-nau2 sui5 siouh-touh--khi3, chit8-e5 lang5 to2 ti7 kheh-thiann phong3-i2 teng2, thau5-khak lai7 be7-su ko7-ko7-lin3 e5 chau2-be2-teng, hit-chun7, goa2 thau5 chit8 pai2 kam2-kak khoann3-tioh8 senn3-mia7 goan5-thau5 e5 kng.
Koh-khah an2-choann2 ma7 siunn7 be7-kau3, koe3 10 goa7 ni5 liau2-au7, ti7 goa7-kok e5 thou2-te7--nih, ti7 goan2 2 e5 lang5 te7-ji7-e5 gin2-a2 beh chhut-si3 e5 chit-chun7, soah e7 koh the2-giam7 tioh8 kang7-khoan2 e5 kng kap jiat8, che ka2-na2 teh ka7 goa2 am3-si7: goa2 iu5-goan5 koh kiann5 ti7 hit-tiau5 chhou-hoat-sim e5 lou7-tou5 teng2-bin7, to7 chhiunn7 10 goa7 ni5 cheng5 hit-e5 siau3-lian5-ke kang7-khoan2.
M7-chai piann3-si3 chhut-lat8 kui2-pai2--a, ka-ti7 e5 i3-chi3 na2-chhiunn7 teh-beh pang-poann5 e5 si5, soah thiann-tioh8 hou7-su7 sio2-chia2 e5 kou2-le7: “Chin ho2! Chin ho2! To7-si7 an2-ne, lai5! Koh chhoan2 nng7 kai2 toa7-khui3! Tan2 au7 chit8 pai2 thiann3 e5 si5-chun7, lan2 to7 cho3 chit8 pai2 ka7 piann3--loh8-khi3! Teh-beh chhut--lai5-a!” Khoann3-tioh8 Bi2-hong5 se3-liap8-chi2 e5 seng-khu kap i tiunn3-ang5 kim3-khui3 e5 kan-khou2 bin7-iong5, sim-lai7 chong2--si7 u7 kong2 be7 chhut-- lai5 e5 m7-kam kap thiann3-thang3. Siong7 boe2--a2, u7 chit8-e5 lo3-kha e5 hou7-su7 sio2-chia2 kui-khi3 poann i2-thau5-a2 lai5 keh kha, khia7 koan5-koan5 siang-chhiu2 chhih8 Bi2-hong5 e5 pak-tou2, chit8-e7 koh chit8-e7, chit8 pai2 soa3-chiap chit8 pai2, m7-chai Bi2-hong5 an2-ne e7-sai2 tong3 joa7 ku2, sim-lai7 bo5 tiunn-ti5 soah hoan5-lo2--khi2-lai5, Bi2-hong5 e5 chhui3-tun5 na2 khui na2 hap8, chhoan2-khui3 ma7 na2 lai5 na2 chhut-lat8, kui-e5 bin7 khoann3--khi2-lai5 toa7-liap8 koann7 se3-liap8 koann7, ka2-na2 chau2 malasong e5 soan2-chhiu2 teh-beh chhiong kau3 chiong-tiam2-soann3 hit-khoan2. Goa2 kan-tann e7-tang3 khia7 tiam3 pinn--a2, sui-bong2 kong2 the3 i chhit-koann7 e5 chhiu2 bo5 chit8-si5 theng5-hioh, sim-lai7 e5 ki5-to2 ma7 m7-bat theng5-khun3--koe3.
Oa5! Oa5! Oa5-a2~~gin2-a2 e5 khau3-siann chhiunn7 tan5 lui5-kong thoan5 jip8 kau3 goa2 hinn7-khang lai7, to7 ti7 che chit8-bio2 lai7, sou2-u7 e5 hou7-su7 sio2-chia2 kin2-tiunn e5 piau2-cheng5 long2 cho3 chit8-e7 khin-sang--loh8-lai5, Bi2-hong5 e5 gan2-sin5 ma7 kang7-khoan2, chhiunn7 tu2 phu5-thau5 e5 jit8-thau5, te7-it-soann3 kng chhio7 jip8-khi3 pun2-chiann5 am3 ou tim5-tang7 e5 chhim-kham3 lai7-te2, chek-si5 kng--khi2-lai5. Goa2, ma7 thau5 chit8 pai2 khoann3-tioh8 hit-e5 goan2 bang7 chiann5 ku2 e5 gin2-a2 Tai7-sam. Sui-bong2 i iau2 koh kui seng-khu hoeh-chui2, m7-koh i si7 goa2 khoann3--koe3 siong7 iong2-kam2 e5 gin2-a2, goa2 an2-ne ka7 Bi2-hong5 kong2, i poe5-phoann7 in a-bo2 kiann5 koe3 chit-toann7 senn3-mia7 e5 lou7, ma7 ka7 in lau7-pe7 ka3 kong2 siann2-mih si7 iong2-khi3. It-tit8 kau3 chit-ma2 goa2 giah8-pit e5 chit-chun7, hit-chiong2 bo5 theng5-khun3 e5 jiat8, na2-chhiunn7 iau2-boe7 ui3 goa2 sim-lai7 the3--khi3, che e7 si7 ka-ti7 chit-si3-lang5 siong7 tin-kui3 e5 chai5-hu3.
Tong-jian5, ka-ti7 ma7 tioh8 kam2-sia7 goan2 e5 thau5 chit8-e5 gin2-a2----Gi5-lian5, na7 m7-si7 i chit gou7-tang lai5, hou7 goa2 chit-e5 chhou-lou2 iu3-chinn2 e5 lau7-pe7 u7 chhi3-giam7 e5 ki-hoe7, goa2 kin-a2-jit8 ma7 bo5 poe5-phoann7 in sio2-ti7 chhut-si3 e5 iong2-khi3, to7 chhin-chhiunn7 i chhut-si3 hit tong-si5 kang7-khoan2, si7 i hou7 goa2 choan2-pian3 seng5-tiong2 e5 ki-hoe7 kap iong2-khi3, hian7-chhu2-si5, goa2 kan-tann siunn7 beh hou7 in 2 e5 chai-iann2, in tui3 goa2 u7 joa7 tiong7-iau3, in 2 e5 gin2-a2 chhut-si3, hou7 chit8-e5 pun2-te2 m7-kann2 seng5-tam senn3-mia7 tang7-tann3 e5 cha-pou gin2-a2, tng2-kut chiann5-cho3 u7 iong2-khi3 koh kann2 tam-tng e5 cha-pou-lang5, ma7 iong7 jin5-seng3 e5 jiat8-cheng5 ka7 hit-pha siong7 sui2 e5 hoe2 tiam2 hou7 toh8.
Au7-ki3:
2002 ni5 12 goeh8 26 chai2-khi2 9 tiam2 27 hun, Tai7-sam ti7 Jit8-pun2 Okayama(Kong-san) Che3-seng-hoe7 Chong2-hap8 Penn7-inn7 8 lau5 hu7-san2-pou7 chhut-si3, thang-a2 goa7 hng7-hng7 hia, u7 goan2 sek8-sai7 e5 Poann3-tian5-soann sio poe5-phoann7.
Che eng3-kai si7 goa2 thau5 chit8 pai2 iong7 ka-ti7 e5 bo2-gi2----Ho7-lo2 Tai5-oan5-oe7, sia2 chiah-ni7 tng5 e5 kou3-su7, giah8-pit e5 chhiong-tong7 si7 ui3 Tai7-sam chhut-si3 hit chit8-khek khai-si2, goa2 chin ng3-bang7 u7 chit8-kang i e7-tang3 khoann3-tioh8 chit-phinn bun5-chiunn, iong7 ka-ti7 siong7 chhin e5 oe7-gi2, li2-kai2 i chhut-si3 e5 si5, in a-pa siong7 kai3 chin-sit8 bo5 un2-moa5 e5 sim-cheng5, chai-iann2 i e5 chhut-si3, hou7 in lau7-pe7 the2-giam7 tioh8 senn3-mia7 lai7-te2 siong7 tit8-chiap e5 kam2-tong7!
